00:06:53.840 --> 00:06:56.570
my 12-year-old dream,
which is to have created

00:06:56.570 --> 00:06:58.240
an interesting gaming company.

00:06:58.240 --> 00:07:01.640
And we get to create product
that people care about,

00:07:01.640 --> 00:07:04.160
